snippet.title: Ambulance Life: A Paramedic Simulator | Bay Side Expansion Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Bay Side Expansion will be available in April, 22nd on PC, PlayStation®5 and Xbox Series X|S.

Welcome to Bay Side, a brand-new district filled with emergencies! Suit up, Paramedic, lives are in your hands!

🔹 New callouts
🔹 New catastrophic event
🔹 Someone always needs saving

Make every second count. Ambulance Life is your chance to save lives. Get in the action! 🚑

Ambulance Life: A Paramedic Simulator is now available on PC, PlayStation®5 and Xbox Series X|S ► https://www.nacongaming.com/en-US/ambulance-life 

Follow us on Twitter ► https://x.com/TheAmbulanceSim
Follow Aesir on Twitter ► https://x.com/AesirInteractiv
